                                    "content": "To demonstrate the methodology, we consider a negative basis position in our fund XAIA Credit Basis II on Lumen Technologies Inc. On 21 May 2021 we bought 4 mm USD bond and matched CDS protection (so- called bullet basis package). The EUR PnL of this position until 17 March 2022 is strongly positive by 313,710 EUR, but mainly because the USD has appreciated with respect to the EUR, with the EUR- USD exchange rate falling from 1.22 to 1.1. Indeed, the number "
